{"tid":282184,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"啟業貨櫃街市 賽後報告","createTime":"2017-06-13T07:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T16:11:20.000Z","uid":80386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dba313c96b61c968e6379e6db0fb8764a85a1fd","tid":282184,"uid":80386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"首先講一講個環境 呢到新開嘅 所以好乾淨企理 但係啲長椅比啲廢老霸住晒 喺到鉗痰搓腳指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先講一間正常嘅 價錢都合理 味道叫正常<br />\n<br />\n粟米火腿手抓餅(有其他料可以揀) $23<br />\n都幾多料 味道正常<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/150738_f1dc547da6640f13e9867e4dd161df86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F150738_f1dc547da6640f13e9867e4dd161df86.jpg&h=4a6e86c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/150740_63ea8f8d0ba8c6bf95ac0fdba3841187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F150740_63ea8f8d0ba8c6bf95ac0fdba3841187.jpg&h=d5d8a539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薯格 $11<br />\n咸到PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/150850_ba9162194912eba0773daee73df7e0a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F150850_ba9162194912eba0773daee73df7e0a4.jpg&h=97054a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n粉仔 搵唔到價錢 收左我$17<br />\n味道正常 不過18座都好味好多<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/150852_a8d51fecb35000bcc293037eaa09cb52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F13%2F150852_a8d51fecb35000bcc293037eaa09cb52.jpg&h=4b50935e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfb58904f6f95fefebbf9ea2b4fd0d9a2d8227c1","tid":282184,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2